title: Renji De Chin!
description:
Description :
        Ren Sonoda, 13 year old middle school girl, is abducted by a UFO one night and she finds she has an extra appendage between her legs in the morning! A space chicken promises to return her to normal, but only if she'll help track down an intergalactic fugitive...

chapters.chapter_name: Chapter 2: Go For It At The Pool
